swVoiceVLANMIB.name: swVoiceVLANMIB
swVoiceVLANMIB.description: The Voice VLAN module MIB for the proprietary enterprise.

swVoiceVlanId.name: swVoiceVlanId
swVoiceVlanId.description: The VLAN ID of the voice VLAN. The voice VLAN is used to asssign VLAN for untagged voice packets. If the value zero is for display only and not configurable, which means there is no voice VLAN on the switch.

swVoivceVlanGlobalState.name: swVoivceVlanGlobalState
swVoivceVlanGlobalState.description: This object indicates the global status of the Voice VLAN. if we enable the voice vlan, we should set the vid first.

swVoiceVlanPriority.name: swVoiceVlanPriority
swVoiceVlanPriority.description: The priority for the voice VLAN ,which is used to distinguish the QoS of the voice traffic from data traffic.

swVoiceVlanAgingTime.name: swVoiceVlanAgingTime
swVoiceVlanAgingTime.description: The aging time for the voice VLAN ,which is used to remove a port from a voice VLAN when the working mode is auto.

swVoiceVlanLogState.name: swVoiceVlanLogState
swVoiceVlanLogState.description: This object indicates the voice VLAN log state.

swVoiceVlanDynamicPortlist.name: swVoiceVlanDynamicPortlist
swVoiceVlanDynamicPortlist.description: The voice VLAN's member ports that dynamically joined the voice VLAN from a learned voice device.

swVoiceVlanDeviceTable.name: swVoiceVlanDeviceTable
swVoiceVlanDeviceTable.description: The Management information of a voice VLAN member ports'device.

swVoiceVlanDeviceEntry.name: swVoiceVlanDeviceEntry
swVoiceVlanDeviceEntry.description: The information from the voice device connected to the switch.

swVoiceVlanDeviceStartTime.name: swVoiceVlanDeviceStartTime
swVoiceVlanDeviceStartTime.description: The time the voice device first connected to the switch.

swVoiceVlanDeviceActiveTime.name: swVoiceVlanDeviceActiveTime
swVoiceVlanDeviceActiveTime.description: The active time of the voice device.

swVoiceVlanOuiTable.name: swVoiceVlanOuiTable
swVoiceVlanOuiTable.description: The Management information of the voice VLAN OUI.

swVoiceVlanOuiEntry.name: swVoiceVlanOuiEntry
swVoiceVlanOuiEntry.description: The management information of the OUI of a voice VLAN domain. An OUI contains information about the type of ip-phone .that can make use of the OUI to check the voice traffic .

swVoiceVlanOuiAddr.name: swVoiceVlanOuiAddr
swVoiceVlanOuiAddr.description: The address of the OUI referring to this SwVoiceVlanOuiEntry.

swVoiceVlanOuiMask.name: swVoiceVlanOuiMask
swVoiceVlanOuiMask.description: The OUI mask indicates the valid bit of the OUI address.

swVoiceVlanOuiRowStatus.name: swVoiceVlanOuiRowStatus
swVoiceVlanOuiRowStatus.description: This object indicates the status of this entry.

swVoiceVlanPortTable.name: swVoiceVlanPortTable
swVoiceVlanPortTable.description: The Management of the voice VLAN function on all bridge ports. Some ports are not member ports of a voice VLAN, but they may be added in auto mode, so this function enables both current voice VLAN member ports and non-VLAN member ports to be managed.

swVoiceVlanPortEntry.name: swVoiceVlanPortEntry
swVoiceVlanPortEntry.description: The Management of the voice VLAN function on ports

swVoiceVlanPortNumber.name: swVoiceVlanPortNumber
swVoiceVlanPortNumber.description: Bridge ports, can be configured with voice VLAN function.

swVoiceVlanPortState.name: swVoiceVlanPortState
swVoiceVlanPortState.description: Port state here indicates whether the port supports the voice VLAN function, we can enable/disable voice vlan function on port.

swVoiceVlanPortMode.name: swVoiceVlanPortMode
swVoiceVlanPortMode.description: Port mode just indicates which mode of voice VLAN function is supported by port. If in auto mode ,the port can be added in to voice vlan automatically when it connect a ip-phone,else the port just added by mannual.
